Package de.btu.openinfra.backend.db Description

This package contains database related stuff which is required to bootstrap the database connections. The class OpenInfraDao implements the database access for all DAO classes and provides the entity manager which is set by the constructor method. Therefore, the class EntityManagerFactoryCache is utilized. You have to extend the following classes in order to create a new database schema: OpenInfraSchemas, EntityManagerFactoryCache

BTU DBIS
